				Companies
			






			Anthem, Inc. is working to transform health care with trusted and caring solutions. Our health plan companies deliver quality products and services that give their members access to the care they need. Anthem's Blue-licensed subsidiaries and their affiliates provide a comprehensive range of group and individual health benefit, life and disability products. Anthem has grown with consistency and reliability in our industry. This performance is the result of strong internal growth, strategic expansion and an approach to managing and growing our business that is guided by a commitment to leadership, innovation and social responsibility. A wide range of products are offered by Anthem's subsidiaries throughout the United States.
		





